repro_steps: Compare direct pm list-all outputs versus linked pm test run outputs for the same command.
resolution: Resolved by PM-context parity controls and mismatch guardrails.
expected_result: Linked PM-command tests reflect equivalent tracker context or fail with explicit mismatch diagnostics.
actual_result: Sandbox-linked PM commands can pass while observing empty or divergent datasets.
